pret = estimatePortReturn(obj,pwgt) estimates the mean of portfolio returns (as the proxy
for portfolio return) for Portfolio, PortfolioCVaR, or PortfolioMAD objects. For details on the
respective workflows when using these different objects, see “Portfolio Object Workflow” on page 4-
18, “PortfolioCVaR Object Workflow” on page 5-16, and “PortfolioMAD Object Workflow” on page 6-
16.
